data.description: Price Adjustment.  Completely updated home in sought-after Broadmoor Subdivision.  Enjoy the serenity of this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home on the covered back patio overlooking the spacious privacy-fenced yard and butterfly garden.  New roof in 2022.  Additional improvements include updated-remodeled guest bath, new durable wood-look flooring, new designer MCM light fixtures, under-cabinet kitchen lights, all new landscaping with fountain, plantation shutters.  The spacious kitchen boasts solid butcher-block counter tops with granite prep station,  abundant cabinet space,  eat-in snack bar, pantry and gas range.  Open concept dining-living room with bonus den-flex room adjoining the kitchen and dining area.  Plenty of closet and storage space in addition to a floored attic and newer outdoor storage building.    Refrigerator to remain.  All outdoor patio furniture to remain unless Buyer opts not to retain it.  Owner-agent.
